about you here.

87
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:11,470
You need to give me a good explanation

88
00:06:11,470 --> 00:06:13,100
for these serious allegations.

89
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:14,340
Ms. Zhen,

90
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:16,670
the management I implemented

91
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:18,500
was to improve the company's work efficiency.

92
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:20,140
These complaint letters

93
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:22,070
are making a mountain out of a molehill.

94
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:24,340
