107
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:56,900
We need to gather more evidence

108
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:59,640
that proves Ma Tianming's abuse of power

109
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:02,240
before we can take action against him.

110
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,840
I will observe his every move

111
