Qin, the hot pot shop downstairs is doing a promotion.

144
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,840
Let's have a meal together after work.

145
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:27,670
Let's go,

146
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,470
Qin. It's very delicious.

147
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:30,870
I'll go next time.

148
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:31,840
Qin.

149
00:09:32,070 --> 00:09:33,070
