152
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:43,100
Mr. Ma. Today is my daughter's birthday.

153
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:45,640
I promised to take her to the park after work.

154
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,640
After I divorced her father,

155
00:09:47,940 --> 00:09:49,240
